            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-7746c4c1a4bc8be8-08e7ce twpub-7746c4c1a4bc8be8-42a937 twpub-7746c4c1a4bc8be8-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\"><i>Author of<br>\n<br>\n“The Shuttle,” “The Making of a Marchioness,” “The Methods of Lady Walderhurst,” “The Lass o’ Lowries,” “Through One Administration,” “Little Lord Fauntleroy,” “A Lady of Quality,” etc.</i></p></div>"
